## Known Technical Debt

1. Lifetime counters (lifetimeEarned, lifetimePaid, lifetimeClawedBack, salesCount30d) are schema
   columns but never updated in code. Deliberately excluded from /api/affiliate/balances response.
   Needs a separate backend step before exposing in UI.

2. Admin UI (Step 8) has no loading state on Approve/Reject buttons during requests. Risk of
   double-click during slow responses. Fix: disable buttons or show spinner while fetch is in flight.

3. AffiliateClick has FK to Affiliate without onDelete: Cascade. Cleanup of test affiliates
   requires manual deleteMany on AffiliateClick first.

4. Admin approve/reject has race condition: findUnique then update is non-atomic. Two concurrent
   admin clicks could double-process. Acceptable for MVP. Fix: updateMany({ where: { id, status:
   pending } }) and check count.

